ef=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2018/09/13/politics/china-trade-war-kudlow/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2Fpolitics%2Fchina-trade-war-kudlow%2Findex.html&d=ft9ksCca5MMv8Buqu4KpWf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=54f83c07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2Fpolitics%2Fchina-trade-war-kudlow%2Findex.html&h=a2027d7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2018/09/13/politics/china-trade-war-kudlow/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\ncnn寫得最清楚<br />\n<br />\nLater on Thursday, Trump tweeted that the United States is &quot;under no pressure to make a deal with China, they are under pressure to make a deal with us.&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1040242677877551104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1040242677877551104&d=ft9ksCca5MMv8Buqu4KpWf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5df5fc7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1040242677877551104&h=5ca60b9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1040242677877551104</a><br />\n<br />\n[Donald J. Trump<br />\n&rlm;<br />\n已認證帳戶<br />\n <br />\n@realDonaldTrump<br />\n跟隨 跟隨 @realDonaldTrump<br />\n更多<br />\n<strong>The Wall Street Journal has it wrong, we are under no pressure to make a deal with China, </strong>they are under pressure to make a deal with us. Our markets are surging, theirs are collapsing. We will soon be taking in Billions in Tariffs &amp; making products at home. If we meet, we meet?<br />\n<br />\n上午7:15 - 2018年9月13日]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>5毛賤鬼會員沒有大大的小妹有咩解釋</strong>"},{"pid":"a8afbddd872a0117047839d2c22ce0370ccd0677","tid":817881,"uid":82717,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"137ff83aa3623c0c5ff8c2db953a4062545c601f","tid":817881,"uid":37197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cit